  "text": "For the 34 potential replacement compounds shown in Figure 1 , the estrogenic activity was analyzed by extracting experimental data and in silico predictions. The reference compound, BPA, and a small subset of the 34 potential replacement molecules for which experimental data were available, were obtained through searching the estrogenic activity database (EADB) [CITATION_1] ; our recently updated database in the endocrine disruptors knowledge base (EDKB) [CITATION_2] .",
